         <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">536.270-1</ph> Solicitations.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
         <p class="- topic/p ">Solicitations containing options shall:</p>
         <ol id="d621e13" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li audience="GSAR"
                otherprops="abc"
                outputclass="Grey_H5_abc"
                xtrf="Grey"
                class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d615e17"
                  outputclass="H5_abc"
                  xtrf="Grey"
                  class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                    Include
appropriate option provisions and clauses when resulting contracts
will provide for the exercise of options (see <xref href="GSAM-536.270-5.dita#id1941D0D606X"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">536.270-5</xref>);</p>
            </li>
            <li audience="GSAR"
                otherprops="abc"
                outputclass="Grey_H5_abc"
                xtrf="Grey"
                class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d615e26"
                  outputclass="H5_abc"
                  xtrf="Grey"
                  class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                   State the
period within which the options may be exercised; and</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                    State
whether the basis of evaluation is inclusive or exclusive of the
options (if exclusive, see <xref href="GSAM-536.270-4.dita#id1941CC006NZ"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">536.270-4</xref>(c)).</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
      </conbody>
